divs: Sighting DetailsI was on my front porch taking pics of the Fulfill Snow Moon on February 25, 2013, and after observing the pics found that there was and unidentifiable object in the pic to the upper left of the moon. My daughter's friend said I should contact authorities about this event
trends: There have been 24 other sightings in Roanoke
There were no other sightings in Roanoke on or around February 25th 2013
Summary: was taking pics of the full snow moon and this object showed up in the pic...lightning showed up in the other
